\h(《Vice Captain》)Your Excellency, the sun is up 
and the visibility is good. 
Escape preparation is complete. \e

\h(《Alfonso》)Hehehe… Oh, really. 
I have finished my preparations as well. \e

\h(《Vice Captain》)P… please!
Your, Your Excellency!!!
What are you doing!? \e

\h(《Alfonso》)This battleship was 
robbed by the air pirates 
because you betrayed us… \e

\h(《Alfonso》)…And to keep my glorious legend 
from being stained with filth… You must die. \e

\h(《Vice Captain》)No… No! Please
forgive me, Your Excellency! \e

\h(《Alfonso》)What choice did I have but 
to dispose of the traitor?  \e

\h(　)So, is that how Valua 
deals with it's people? \e

\h(《Vyse》)We will be taking care of her from here.
However…
I have one more thing to do before we leave. \e

\h(《Vyse》)As a fellow sailor…
I can't allow you to carry on like this. 
Draw your blade, Alfonso！\e

\h(《Alfonso》)Heh… You dare speak to 
me with such an insolent tone? 
I shall have your head for it! \e

\h(《Alfonso》)You will regret ever 
defying me. 
Antonio! \e

\h(《Alfonso》)He's my personal warbeast.  
I was going to leave him here, but it seems 
I've found a use for him after all…\e

\h(《Alfonso》)Antonio! 
Skewer those air pirates with 
your horns! \e
